---
title: Arroz Con Pollo with Avocado, Tomato, and Lime Crema
description: Arroz con pollo simply means “chicken and rice” in Spanish, which doesn’t begin to describe all of the other delicious things going on in this recipe. Everything gets amped up with a sprinkling of our smoky Mexican seasoning, which adds warm, sultry flavors throughout. Then the toppings—creamy slices of avocado, tangy bursts of tomato, and a zesty lime crema—bring contrast and excitement.
